            <circle cx="18" cy="9" r="3" fill="#52b043" opacity="0.8"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="5" fill="#52b043" opacity="0.9"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="2.5" fill="#ffffff" opacity="0.9"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:1">Volt IVR</div>
            <div style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);letter-spacing:1px;margin-top:4px;text-transform:uppercase">by Unitech International</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h1>Powering <span>Efficiency</span> &amp; Sustainability</h1>
        <p>Stop overpaying on energy. Volt IVR cross-checks every utility invoice against your supply contract, network tariffs, consumption history and an extensive set of industry billing rules and compliance criteria. Whether errors are happening right now or buried in years of historic supply, Volt IVR will find them. Spot live billing mistakes as they happen, reconcile historic overcharges, and ensure every recoverable charge is identified and claimed.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:24px;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);letter-spacing:0.5px">Directly enabling the recovery of millions for our customers across the UK.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="auth-left-footer">
        &copy; 2026 Unitech International Ltd &middot; Company No. 10611226<br>
        <a href="tel:02081294748">020 8129 4748</a> &middot; <a href="mailto:info@unitechinternational.co.uk">info@unitechinternational.co.uk</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="auth-right">
    <div class="auth-box">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:24px">
        <svg class="atom-svg" width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 60 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <ellipse cx="30" cy="30" rx="24" ry="9" fill="none" stroke="#52b043" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.85"/>
          <ellipse cx="30" cy="30" rx="24" ry="9" fill="none" stroke="#52b043" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.85" transform="rotate(60 30 30)"/>
          <ellipse cx="30" cy="30" rx="24" ry="9" fill="none" stroke="#52b043" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.85" transform="rotate(120 30 30)"/>
          <circle cx="54" cy="30" r="3" fill="#8de87a"/><circle cx="42" cy="9" r="3" fill="#52b043"/>
          <circle cx="18" cy="9" r="3" fill="#52b043" opacity="0.8"/>
          <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="5" fill="#52b043" opacity="0.9"/>
          <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="2.5" fill="#ffffff" opacity="0.9"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:var(--g);letter-spacing:1px;line-height:1">Volt IVR</div>
          <div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3);margin-top:3px">by Unitech International</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="auth-title">Client <span>Portal</span></div>
